// src/pages/FraudPage.jsx import React, { useState } from 'react'; import { AlertTriangle, Clock, TrendingUp, Filter, Download } from 'lucide-react'; const FraudPage = () => { const [selectedAlert, setSelectedAlert] = useState(null); const [filterPriority, setFilterPriority] = useState('all'); const fraudAlerts = [ { id: 'F001', title: 'Multiple Refund Pattern', priority: 'High', score: 92, description: 'Customer initiated 8 refunds in 24 hours', timestamp: '2 hours ago', category: 'Refund Abuse', customerId: 'C123456789', amount: '$2,347.89' }, { id: 'F002', title: 'Account Takeover Attempt', priority: 'High', score: 89, description: 'Login from suspicious IP with different device', timestamp: '3 hours ago', category: 'Account Security', customerId: 'C987654321', amount: '$1,892.45' }, { id: 'F003', title: 'Credit Card Testing', priority: 'Medium', score: 76, description: 'Multiple failed payment attempts with different cards', timestamp: '5 hours ago', category: 'Payment Fraud', customerId: 'C456789123', amount: '$156.99' }, { id: 'F004', title: 'Shipping Address Mismatch', priority: 'Medium', score: 68, description: 'Billing and shipping addresses in different countries', timestamp: '6 hours ago', category: 'Address Verification', customerId: 'C789123456', amount: '$789.33' }, { id: 'F005', title: 'Velocity Check Failure', priority: 'Low', score: 54, description: 'Unusual purchase frequency detected', timestamp: '8 hours ago', category: 'Behavioral', customerId: 'C321654987', amount: '$234.56' }, { id: 'F006', title: 'Duplicate Transaction Pattern', priority: 'Medium', score: 71, description: 'Same items purchased multiple times rapidly', timestamp: '12 hours ago', category: 'Transaction Pattern', customerId: 'C654987321', amount: '$445.67' } ]; const filteredAlerts = filterPriority === 'all' ? fraudAlerts : fraudAlerts.filter(alert => alert.priority === filterPriority); const getPriorityColor = (priority) => { switch (priority) { case 'High': return 'bg-red-600 text-white'; case 'Medium': return 'bg-yellow-500 text-black'; case 'Low': return 'bg-green-500 text-white'; default: return 'bg-neutral-600 text-white'; } }; const getScoreColor = (score) => { if (score >= 80) return 'text-red-400'; if (score >= 60) return 'text-yellow-400'; return 'text-green-400'; }; const stats = { totalAlerts: fraudAlerts.length, highPriority: fraudAlerts.filter(a => a.priority === 'High').length, mediumPriority: fraudAlerts.filter(a => a.priority === 'Medium').length, lowPriority: fraudAlerts.filter(a => a.priority === 'Low').length, totalAmount: fraudAlerts.reduce((sum, alert) => sum + parseFloat(alert.amount.replace('$', '').replace(',', '')), 0) }; return (

setSelectedAlert(alert)} className="bg-neutral-700 rounded-lg p-5 hover:bg-neutral-600 transition-all duration-200 cursor-pointer border border-neutral-600 hover:border-neutral-500" >
Alert {alert.id} {alert.priority}

{alert.title}

{alert.description}

Customer ID: {alert.customerId}
Amount: {alert.amount}
Category: {alert.category}
{alert.timestamp}
Risk Score: {alert.score}%
))}
{/* Selected Alert Details Modal */} {selectedAlert && (

Alert Details - {selectedAlert.id}

{selectedAlert.priority}

{selectedAlert.score}%

{selectedAlert.customerId}

{selectedAlert.amount}

{selectedAlert.description}

)}
); }; export default FraudPage;
